message: "If you use this software or build on the techniques described here, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "JSAgent: An AI Agent for Hard Mathematical Optimization"
authors:
  - family-names: Sung
    given-names: Jongmin
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1405-0119"
url: "https://github.com/jmsung/einstein"
